title: Salisbury Steak-Style Beyond Meat® Patties and Mash with Shallot Gravy and Apple Salad
description: We're breaking with tradition and making this classic dish with Beyond Meat® instead of beef. Shallot gravy is poured over top and creamy mash and a refreshing side salad come alongside. The result is hearty, tasty and balanced — all in one meal!

